    "Our search strategy included Scopus, a popular meta-level research database, as well as two renowned computer science publishers, namely ACM and IEEE.",
    "Scopus indexes a range of relevant computer science databases, such as ACM, DBLP Computer Science Bibliography, IEEExplore, and SpringerLink, making it an appropriate choice for xAI research.",
    "By supplementing our search with research directly from ACM and IEEE, we aimed to achieve a high coverage of relevant studies.",
    "Figure 2 describes our filtering steps of the initial literature.",
